    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A budget-friendly, no-nonsense vehicle that offers dependable basic transportation and excellent value for the price. This car shows its age, but it remains a practical choice for a first-time buyer, commuter, or anyone looking for an affordable runabout with room to make it their own. Priced to reflect condition while still delivering real everyday usefulness.",
      "price": 7950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation, a backup vehicle, or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s been a dependable runner for us and still has good value for the right buyer. If you want something affordable without spending a fortune, this could be a great fit. Priced to sell and ready for its next home.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with a strong-running engine, smooth-shifting transmission, and a chassis that feels planted on the road. It shows cosmetic wear and needs attention in places, but it\u2019s a straightforward platform with good bones, responsive throttle, and plenty of usable life for someone who wants an affordable car to drive, sort, or build. A great opportunity for a hands-on buyer looking for dependable mechanical fundamentals at an accessible price.",
      "price": 7800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Cosmetically rough, priced to move. First serious buyer gets it.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true underdog with personality, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who loves a hands-on project, needs an inexpensive set of wheels, or wants a budget-friendly ride with unmistakable presence. There\u2019s a certain charm here you just don\u2019t get from bland, forgettable commuters\u2014this one feels like it still has stories left to tell. If you appreciate value, grit, and potential, this is a chance to bring home something with real spirit at a price that leaves room for your vision.",
      "price": 6400.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
